body:
Hello @josharoon! Thanks for updating the PR.



Cheers ! There are no PEP8 issues in this Pull Request. :beers: 

##### Comment last updated on November 14, 2017 at 21:11 Hours UTC

Thanks. This is an internal class that we've backported from python3. I suspect the docstring was just copied over from the standard library.

This may not be a super useful change since

- it's not included in pandas' documentation
- pandas developers would just reference the offical python docs (I think)

If you are interested in contributing to the docs, we have a bunch of known issues tagged: https://github.com/pandas-dev/pandas/issues?q=is%3Aopen+is%3Aissue+label%3ADocs
